title: Cowboy Junkies 2000-06-13 @ Moore Theater - Seattle, WA
description:
So, this show comes from the 2000 Waltz Across America tour, a tour that gave us a lot of quality performances from the band. This show is from Seattle and features some great songs, including "Ring on the Sill," the always welcome "Upon Still Waters," and "Dragging Hooks," which had just been debuted a few weeks earlier in New Mexico.

 

Plus, quite frankly, this show contains "Something More Besides You" for the first encore, so it has two of my all time favorite Junkies&#039; tunes ("Ring" being the other). I remember the excitement I felt when I saw this setlist and popped the show in to listen to after receiving it. Hopefully you&#039;ll all like it as well.
